  <para style="h">2 Timoseewo</para>
  <para style="toc1">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Omutukuvu Eyookubiri eri Timoseewo</para>
  <para style="toc2">2 Timoseewo</para>
  <para style="toc3">2Ti</para>
  <para style="mt2">Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo Omutukuvu Eyookubiri eri</para>
  <para style="mt1">Timoseewo</para>
  <para style="imt">Ennyanjula</para>
  <para style="ip">Eno y’ebbaluwa eyookubiri Pawulo Omutukuvu gye yawandiikira Timoseewo, eyali omulabirizi ow’olubereberye mu Kkanisa y’omu Efeso. Yagiwandiikira mu Ruumi ng’asibiddwa olw’okubuulira Enjiri, wakati w’emyaka <char style="sc">ad</char> 67 ne 68, era ng’asemberedde ekiseera ky’okuttibwa. Ebbaluwa ya Pawulo eno eri ng’eddaame lye erisembayo, lye yaweereza omuyigirizwa we era mukozi munne omwagalwa Timoseewo nti newaakubadde ng’obulamu bwe obw’oku nsi buyinza okuggwaawo, nga bamusse, Katonda amutegekedde obulamu obutaggwaawo obumulindiridde mu ggulu. Era Pawulo ayigiriza ku Katonda nga bw’ali omwesigwa eyamukulembera n’amuyisa mu bulamu bwe bwonna, era ayogera ne ku nnaku ez’akabi ezigenda okujja, ekiyinza okuleetera abantu okuva ku mazima ne bagaana okukkiriza Katonda nga bw’ali Mukama wa byonna. Pawulo abuulirira Timoseewo okubeera omunywevu ng’ebiseera ebizibu eby’okuyigganyizibwa bituuse, ayongere bwongezi okubuulira Enjiri ey’amazima.</para>
  <para style="ie"/>
  <chapter number="1" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:1 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2CO 1:1">2Ko 1:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 3:6">Bef 3:6</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 6:19">1Ti 6:19</ref></char>
    </note>Nze, Pawulo, omutume wa Kristo Yesu olw’okwagala kwa Katonda, ng’okusuubiza bwe kuli okw’obulamu obuli mu Kristo Yesu, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:2 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 16:1">Bik 16:1</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:2">1Ti 1:2</ref></char></note>nkuwandiikira ggwe Timoseewo omwana wange omwagalwa, nga nkwagaliza ekisa n’okusaasirwa, n’emirembe ebiva eri Katonda Kitaffe, ne Kristo Yesu Mukama waffe.</para>
  <para style="s1">Okwebaza n’Okugumya</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="3" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:3 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:8">Bar 1:8</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 1:10">Bar 1:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Neebaza Katonda gwe mpeereza mu mwoyo omulungi nga bajjajjange bwe baakola, nga nkujjukira obutayosa mu kusaba kwange emisana n’ekiro. <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:4 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 20:37">Bik 20:37</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 4:9">2Ti 4:9</ref></char></note>Bwe nzijukira amaziga go ne neegomba okukulaba ndyoke nzijule essanyu. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:5 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:5">1Ti 1:5</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 16:1">Bik 16:1</ref></char></note>Nzijukira okukkiriza kwo okw’amazima olubereberye okwali mu jjajjaawo Looyi ne mukadde wo Ewuniike; era nga nkakasiza ddala nga naawe okulina. <verse number="6" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:6 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 4:14">1Ti 4:14</ref></char></note>Kyenva nkujjukiza okuseesanga ekirabo kya Katonda ekiri mu ggwe kye yakuwa, bwe nakussaako emikono gyange. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:7 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:15">Bar 8:15</ref></char></note>Kubanga Mwoyo wa Katonda, gwe yatuwa tatufuula bati, wabula atuwa amaanyi, n’okwagala era n’okwegendereza.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:8 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MRK 8:38">Mak 8:38</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 1:16">Bar 1:16</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 3:1">Bef 3:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2TI 2:3">2Ti 2:3</ref>, <ref loc="2TI 2:9">9</ref>; <ref loc="2TI 4:5">4:5</ref></char>
    </note>Noolwekyo tokwatibwa nsonyi kwogera ku bya Mukama waffe, wadde ku nze omusibe we, wabula naawe bonaabona olw’Enjiri ng’oyambibwa amaanyi ga Katonda, <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:28">Bar 8:28</ref></char></note>eyatulokola n’atuyita tubeere babe. Ekyo yakikola nga tasinziira ku bikolwa byaffe, wabula ng’asinziira mu kuyitibwa okutukuvu, si ng’ebikolwa byaffe bwe biri, naye olw’ekigendererwa kye ye, n’ekisa kye, kye yatukwatirwa ng’ayita mu Kristo Yesu okuva edda n’edda Lyonna. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:9">Bef 1:9</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 15:26">1Ko 15:26</ref>, <ref loc="1CO 15:54">54</ref></char></note>Kaakano ekisa ekyo kyolesebbwa mu kulabika kw’Omulokozi waffe Kristo Yesu eyaggyawo okufa, n’aleeta obulamu obutazikirizibwa ng’ayita mu Njiri, <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:11 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 2:7">1Ti 2:7</ref></char></note>gye nalonderwa okugisaasaanya, n’okuba omutume, era omuyigiriza, <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:12 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 6:20">1Ti 6:20</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false">nny 18</char></note>era kyenva mbonaabona bwe ntyo. Kyokka sikwatibwa nsonyi, kubanga mmanyi gwe nakkiriza, era nkakasa nti ayinza okukuuma ekyo kye namuteresa okutuusa olunaku luli.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:13 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="TIT 1:9">Tit 1:9</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 1:14">1Ti 1:14</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Gobereranga ebigambo ebireeta obulamu bye wawulira njogera, mu kukkiriza ne mu kwagala mu Kristo Yesu. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 8:9">Bar 8:9</ref></char></note>Ekintu ekirungi eky’omuwendo kye wateresebwa kikuumenga ng’oyambibwa Mwoyo Mutukuvu abeera mu ffe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="15" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:15 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2TI 4:10">2Ti 4:10</ref>, <ref loc="2TI 4:11">11</ref>, <ref loc="2TI 4:16">16</ref></char>
    </note>Kino okimanyi, ng’ab’omu Asiya bonna banjabulira, mu abo mwe muli Fugero ne Kerumogene.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="16" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">1:16 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="2TI 4:19">2Ti 4:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mukama akwatirwe ekisa ab’omu nnyumba ya Onesifolo, kubanga yambeesabeesa emirundi mingi era teyankwatirwa nsonyi kubanga ndi musibe; <verse number="17" style="v"/>bwe yatuuka e Ruumi, yafuba nnyo okunnoonya era n’anzuula. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">1:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="HEB 6:10">Beb 6:10</ref></char></note>Mukama amukwatirwe ekisa ku lunaku luli. Era gw’omanyi bulungi nnyo byonna bye yakola mu Efeso.</para>
  <chapter number="2" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Omuserikale Omwesigwa owa Kristo</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="EPH 6:10">Bef 6:10</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Noolwekyo mwana wange nywereranga mu kisa ekiri mu Kristo Yesu. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:2 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 1:13">2Ti 1:13</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 6:12">1Ti 6:12</ref></char></note>Ebyo bye wawulira nga njogera mu maaso g’abajulirwa abangi biyigirizenga abantu abeesigwa, abalisobola okubiyigiriza abalala. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:18">1Ti 1:18</ref></char></note>Naawe bonaabonanga ng’omuserikale omulungi owa Kristo Yesu. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Tewali muserikale ng’ali ku lutalo eyeeyingiza mu mitawaana gy’abantu abaabulijjo, alyoke asiimibwe oyo eyamuwandiika. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 9:25">1Ko 9:25</ref></char></note>Omuntu yenna eyeetaba mu mizannyo gy’empaka, taweebwa buwanguzi bw’atagoberera biragiro bya mizannyo egyo. <verse number="6" style="v"/>Omulimi ategana ennyo y’asaanira okufuna ku bibala ebibereberye. <verse number="7" style="v"/>Kale lowooza ku bye ŋŋamba; Mukama ajja kukuwa okutegeera byonna.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="8" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:8 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 2:24">Bik 2:24</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 1:1">Mat 1:1</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">c </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 2:16">Bar 2:16</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Jjukira nga Yesu Kristo ow’omu zzadde lya Dawudi yazuukira mu bafu ng’Enjiri gye ntegeeza bw’egamba. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 9:16">Bik 9:16</ref></char></note>Olw’Enjiri eyo, kyenva mbonaabona n’ensibibwa ng’omukozi w’ebibi. Naye ekigambo kya Katonda kyo tekisibiddwa. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:24">Bak 1:24</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 4:17">2Ko 4:17</ref></char></note>Kyenva ngumira ebintu byonna olw’abalonde nabo balyoke balokolebwe era bafune, n’ekitiibwa ekitaggwaawo ekiri mu Kristo Yesu.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="11" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:11 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 6:2-11">Bar 6:2-11</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ekigambo kino kyesigwa ekigamba nti:</para>
  <para style="q1">“Obanga twafiira wamu naye,</para>
  <para style="q2">era tulibeera balamu wamu naye.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="12" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:12 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 8:17">Bar 8:17</ref>; <ref loc="1PE 4:13">1Pe 4:13</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="MAT 10:33">Mat 10:33</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Obanga tugumiikiriza awamu naye, era tulifugira wamu naye.</para>
  <para style="q2">Obanga tumwegaana era naye alitwegaana.</para>
  <para style="q1">
    <verse number="13" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:13 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="NUM 23:19">Kbl 23:19</ref>; <ref loc="ROM 3:3">Bar 3:3</ref></char>
    </note>Ffe bwe tutaba beesigwa, ye aba mwesigwa,</para>
  <para style="q2">kubanga teyeewakanya.”</para>
  <para style="s1">Omukozi Katonda gw’asiima</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:14 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 6:4">1Ti 6:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Ebyo bijjukizenga abantu ng’obakuutirira mu maaso ga Katonda, beewalenga okuwakana okutalina mugaso, nga bakyamya abo abawuliriza. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EPH 1:13">Bef 1:13</ref>; <ref loc="JAS 1:18">Yak 1:18</ref></char></note>Fubanga okweraga ng’osiimibwa Katonda, ng’oli mukozi akola ebitakuswaza, era nga weekuumira mu kkubo ery’obubaka obw’amazima. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="TIT 3:9">Tit 3:9</ref></char></note>Weewalenga ebigambo ebinyooma era ebitaliimu nsa, kubanga abantu bibongera bwongezi mu butatya Katonda. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:20">1Ti 1:20</ref></char></note>Era ebigambo byabwe birisaasaana nga kookolo; mu abo mwe muli Kumenayo ne Fireeto, <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:18 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:19">1Ti 1:19</ref></char></note>abaakyama ne bava ku mazima, nga bagamba nti okuzuukira kwabaawo dda, era waliwo abamu be bakyamizza. <verse number="19" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:19 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ISA 28:16">Is 28:16</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="JHN 10:14">Yk 10:14</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 1:2">1Ko 1:2</ref></char></note>Kyokka omusingi Katonda gwe yateekawo mugumu, era gulina akabonero kano: “Mukama amanyi ababe.” Era nti: “Buli ayatula erinnya lya Mukama ave mu butali butuukirivu.”</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:20 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 9:21">Bar 9:21</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mu nnyumba ennene temubaamu bintu bya zaabu na ffeeza byokka, naye mubaamu n’eby’emiti, era n’eby’ebbumba. Ebimu bikozesebwa emirimu egy’ekitiibwa, n’ebirala egitali gya kitiibwa. <verse number="21" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:21 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 3:17">2Ti 3:17</ref></char></note>Noolwekyo buli eyeewala ebintu ebyo ebitali bya kitiibwa anaabanga ow’ekitiibwa, atukuziddwa, asaanira okukozesebwa mukama we, olw’omulimu omulungi.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">2:22 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 1:14">1Ti 1:14</ref>; <ref loc="1TI 6:11">6:11</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 1:5">1Ti 1:5</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Naye ddukanga okwegomba okubi okw’ekivubuka, ogobererenga obutuukirivu, n’okukkiriza, n’okwagalana era n’emirembe awamu n’abo abasaba Mukama n’omutima omulongoofu. <verse number="23" style="v"/>Weewalenga empaka ez’obusirusiru, ezitaliimu magezi, kubanga omanyi nti zivaamu okulwana. <verse number="24" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:24 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 3:2">1Ti 3:2</ref>, <ref loc="1TI 3:3">3</ref></char></note>Omuddu wa Mukama tasaana kulwana, wabula okuba omukkakkamu eri bonna, n’okuba omuyigiriza omulungi agumiikiriza, <verse number="25" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:25 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 2:4">1Ti 2:4</ref></char></note>era aluŋŋamya n’obwetoowaze abo abamuwakanya, oboolyawo Katonda alibawa okwenenya, ne bamanya amazima, <verse number="26" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">2:26 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 3:7">1Ti 3:7</ref></char></note>ne bava mu mutego gwa Setaani gwe baguddemu abakozese by’ayagala, ne badda engulu mu kutegeera kwabwe.</para>
  <chapter number="3" style="c"/>
  <para style="s1">Ennaku ez’Oluvannyuma</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 4:1">1Ti 4:1</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Naye tegeera kino nga mu nnaku ez’oluvannyuma walibaawo ebiseera ebizibu. <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:2 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 3:3">1Ti 3:3</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:30">Bar 1:30</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 1:30">Bar 1:30</ref></char></note>Kubanga abantu baliba nga beefaako bokka, nga balulunkanira ensimbi, nga beepanka, nga beekuluntaza, nga boogera ebibi, era nga tebawulira bazadde baabwe, nga tebeebaza, nga tebatya Katonda, <verse number="3" style="v"/>nga tebaagalana era nga tebatabagana, nga bawaayiriza, nga tebeegendereza, nga bakambwe, nga tebaagala birungi, <verse number="4" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:4 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 3:6">1Ti 3:6</ref></char></note>nga ba nkwe, nga baagala eby’amasanyu okusinga bwe baagala Katonda; <verse number="5" style="v"/>nga balina ekifaananyi eky’okutya Katonda so nga tebakkiriza maanyi gaakyo. Abantu ab’engeri eyo obeewalanga.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:6 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="JUD 1:4">Yud 4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mu abo mulimu abasensera mu mayumba ne bawamba abakazi abanafu mu mwoyo abazitoowereddwa ebibi, era abawalulwa okwegomba okubi okwa buli ngeri, <verse number="7" style="v"/>abayiga bulijjo, kyokka ne batatuuka ku kutegeerera ddala amazima, <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:8 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 7:11">Kuv 7:11</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 13:8">Bik 13:8</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 6:5">1Ti 6:5</ref></char></note>nga Yane ne Yambere abaawakanya Musa, ne bano bwe batyo bawakanya amazima. Be bantu abaayonooneka ebirowoozo, abatakyalina kukkiriza kutuufu. <verse number="9" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:9 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="EXO 7:12">Kuv 7:12</ref></char></note>Kyokka tebaliiko gye balaga, kubanga obusirusiru bwabwe bujja kumanyibwa abantu bonna, ng’obwa abasajja abo bwe bwamanyibwa.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="10" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">3:10 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="1TI 4:6">1Ti 4:6</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Naye ggwe wagoberera nnyo okuyigiriza kwange, n’empisa zange, ne kye nduubirira, n’okukkiriza kwange n’okubonaabona kwange n’okwagala kwange, n’okugumiikiriza kwange, <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:11 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 13:14">Bik 13:14</ref>, <ref loc="ACT 13:50">50</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2CO 11:23-27">2Ko 11:23-27</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 34:19">Zab 34:19</ref></char></note>n’okuyigganyizibwa n’okubonyaabonyezebwa ebyantukako mu Antiyokiya, ne mu Ikoniya ne mu Lisitula, okuyigganyizibwa kwe nayigganyizibwa, kyokka Mukama n’amponya mu byonna. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 14:22">Bik 14:22</ref></char></note>Era bonna abaagala okuba mu bulamu obutya Katonda mu Kristo Yesu, banaayigganyizibwanga. <verse number="13" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:13 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 2:16">2Ti 2:16</ref></char></note>Naye abakozi b’ebibi n’abalimba abeefuula okuba ekyo kye batali balyeyongera okuba ababi, ne babuzaabuza abalala, era nabo ne babula. <verse number="14" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:14 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 1:13">2Ti 1:13</ref></char></note>Kyokka ggwe nywereranga mu ebyo bye wayiga era n’obikkiririza ddala, ng’omanyi abaabikuyigiriza bwe bali. <verse number="15" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:15 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 1:5">2Ti 1:5</ref></char></note>Kubanga okuva mu buto bwo wamanya Ebyawandiikibwa Ebitukuvu ebiyinza okukufuula ow’amagezi, n’olokolebwa olw’okukkiriza Kristo Yesu. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2PE 1:20">2Pe 1:20</ref>, <ref loc="2PE 1:21">21</ref></char></note>Ebyawandiikibwa Ebitukuvu byonna, Katonda ye yabiruŋŋamya nga biwandiikibwa, era bigasa mu kuyigiriza, mu kunenya, mu kuluŋŋamya ne mu kubuuliranga omuntu abe omutuukirivu, <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">3:17 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 6:11">1Ti 6:11</ref></char></note>omuntu wa Katonda alyoke abe ng’atuukiridde, ng’alina byonna ebyetaagibwa okukola buli mulimu omulungi.</para>
  <chapter number="4" style="c"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="1" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:1 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 10:42">Bik 10:42</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nkukuutirira mu maaso ga Katonda ne Kristo Yesu, anaatera okusalira abalamu n’abafu omusango, era n’olw’okujja kwe, n’olw’obwakabaka bwe, <verse number="2" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:2 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="GAL 6:6">Bag 6:6</ref></char></note>buuliranga ekigambo kya Katonda, ng’oli mwetegefu mu kiseera ekituufu n’ekitali kituufu, ng’olaga ebikwekeddwa, ng’onenya, ng’ozaamu amaanyi, wakati mu kugumiikiriza, n’okubonaabona okungi, n’okuyigiriza. <verse number="3" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:3 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:10">1Ti 1:10</ref></char></note>Kubanga ekiseera kijja lwe baligaana okuwulira enjigiriza entuufu, era olw’okugoberera okwegomba kwabwe balyekuŋŋaanyiza abayigiriza, abalibayigiriza bye baagala, okuwulira. <verse number="4" style="v"/>Baligaana okuwuliriza eby’amazima, ne bagoberera enfumo obufumo. <verse number="5" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:5 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 21:8">Bik 21:8</ref></char></note>Naye ggwe weefugenga mu bintu byonna, ogumirenga ebizibu, ng’okola omulimu ogw’omubuulizi w’enjiri, ng’otuukiririza ddala obuweereza bwo.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="6" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:6 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 2:17">Baf 2:17</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="PHP 1:23">Baf 1:23</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nze kaakano mpebwayo, era ekiseera kyange eky’okuva ku nsi kituuse. <verse number="7" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:7 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1TI 1:18">1Ti 1:18</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1CO 9:24">1Ko 9:24</ref></char></note>Nnwanye okulwana okulungi, mmalirizza olugendo lwange, nkuumye okukkiriza kwange. <verse number="8" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:8 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 1:5">Bak 1:5</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 1:12">2Ti 1:12</ref></char></note>Kye nsigazza kwe kufuna engule ey’obutuukirivu enterekeddwa, Mukama omulamuzi omutuukirivu gy’alimpeera ku lunaku luli. Taligiwa nze nzekka, naye aligiwa n’abo bonna abeegomba okujja kwe.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="9" style="v"/>Fuba okujja amangu gye ndi. <verse number="10" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:10 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 4:14">Bak 4:14</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="1JN 2:15">1Yk 2:15</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 16:6">Bik 16:6</ref></char></note>Kubanga Dema yandekawo ng’ayagala omulembe gwa kaakano, n’agenda e Sessaloniika. Kulesuke yagenda Ggalatiya ne Tito n’agenda e Dalumatiya. <verse number="11" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:11 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="COL 4:14">Bak 4:14</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="2TI 1:15">2Ti 1:15</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">c </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 12:12">Bik 12:12</ref></char></note>Lukka yekka y’ali nange. Ggyayo Makko omuleete, kubanga annyamba nnyo mu buweereza. <verse number="12" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:12 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 20:4">Bik 20:4</ref></char></note>Tukiko n’amutuma mu Efeso. <verse number="13" style="v"/>Bw’obanga ojja ondeeteranga omunagiro gwange gwe naleka e Tulowa ewa Kappo. Ondeeteranga n’emizingo gy’ebitabo, na ddala egyo egy’amaliba.</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="14" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:14 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 19:33">Bik 19:33</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ROM 12:19">Bar 12:19</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Alegezanda, omuweesi w’ebikomo yankola ebyettima bingi. Mukama alimusasula olw’ebikolwa bye. <verse number="15" style="v"/>Naawe mwekuume, kubanga yawakanya nnyo ebigambo byaffe. <verse number="16" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:16 </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 7:60">Bik 7:60</ref></char></note>Mu kuwoza kwange okwasooka, tewaali n’omu yajja kubeera nange, bonna banjabulira. Nsaba Katonda ekyo kireme kubavunaanibwa. <verse number="17" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:17 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 23:11">Bik 23:11</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ACT 9:15">Bik 9:15</ref></char></note>Kyokka Mukama waffe yabeera nange, n’ampa amaanyi, ne nsobola okutegeereza ddala Abaamawanga bonna Enjiri ne bagiwulira, bw’atyo n’anziggya mu kamwa k’empologoma. <verse number="18" style="v"/><note caller="-" style="x"><char style="xo" closed="false">4:18 a </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="PSA 121:7">Zab 121:7</ref> </char><char style="xo" closed="false">b </char><char style="xt" closed="false"><ref loc="ROM 11:36">Bar 11:36</ref></char></note>Era Mukama anamponyanga mu buli kabi, era alintuusa mirembe mu bwakabaka bwe. Mukama agulumizibwenga emirembe n’emirembe. Amiina.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="s1">Okulamusa n’Omukisa</para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="19" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:19 </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 18:2">Bik 18:2</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Nnamusiza Pulisika ne Akula n’ab’omu maka ga Onesifolo.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="20" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:20 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 19:22">Bik 19:22</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="ACT 20:4">Bik 20:4</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Erasuto yasigalayo mu Kkolinso, ate Tulofiimo namuleka mu Mireeto nga mulwadde. <verse number="21" style="v"/>Fuba ojje ng’ebiseera by’obutiti tebinnaba kutuuka.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">Ewubulo akulamusizza, ne Pudente, ne Lino, ne Kulawudiya, n’abooluganda bonna.</para>
  <para style="b"/>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="22" style="v"/>
    <note caller="-" style="x">
      <char style="xo" closed="false">4:22 a </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="GAL 6:18">Bag 6:18</ref>; <ref loc="PHM 1:25">Fir 25</ref> </char>
      <char style="xo" closed="false">b </char>
      <char style="xt" closed="false">
        <ref loc="COL 4:18">Bak 4:18</ref>
      </char>
    </note>Mukama waffe abeerenga n’omwoyo gwo. Ekisa kibeerenga nammwe mwenna.</para>
</usx>
